text: Very nice boarding pier, hassle free. Friendly staff
Very efficient, very clean and organized.

Handy when taking a cruise from the Port of Tampa, you can walk to the port from this location where you can pick up or return Alamo cars.
Although the place looks old and the service is not the best, it is very convenient: they say they have a van that leaves at the port, but they told me that it had already left and at no time did they tell me if there would be another one or any interest in informing me, but there are certain people, anyway I left my family at the port with the car and I went to leave it and from there I walked back
